Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:47.45,Default,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\i1}SLF{\i0}{\i0} Theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:50.20,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\an1\i1\b1\c&HF1FBFD&\3c&H3D717E&\bord4.5\pos(615,870)}Is the Food Bad in {\i1}SLF{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:48.91,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Mini!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:54.79,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Oh, how I love carrots!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.79,0:23:58.50,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,They are truly the greatest of foods!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:01.46,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,The taste, the texture, the shape, the color!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:04.63,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,There has never been a food \Nmore perfect than the carrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.63,0:24:06.72,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Don't you agree, Sunraku-sa—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.22,0:24:10.68,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,S-Sunraku-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:12.64,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Are you eating {\i1}all{\i0} of those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.64,0:24:13.47,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:16.89,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Apparently, there're flavor \Nlimiters in this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:19.27,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Flavor limiters?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:23.90,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It might not make sense \Nto an NPC like you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.90,0:24:26.40,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Let's say there're limiters \Non pioneers' tongues,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.40,0:24:30.87,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,so anything we eat just tastes \Nvaguely sweet, spicy, or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.87,0:24:36.04,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,But I heard you can remove flavor \Nlimiters if you eat a ton of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.12,0:24:39.75,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.75,0:24:42.29,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,But I do hope you don't gorge yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.54,0:24:44.00,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.00,0:24:46.38,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}The flavor's doesn't change, \Nno matter how much I eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.22,0:24:50.97,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,I brought this one special \Nfrom the Palace of Rabituza!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.80,0:24:57.14,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Boy, I wish I could enjoy food that much...
